record.dcterms:description: Baseball team, 1890, Fredericksburg. - Schuylkill Seminary was established in Reading in 1881, moved to Fredericksburg in 1886, then returned to Reading in 1902. It was renamed Schuylkill College in 1923, and merged with Albright College in 1928.
